WEBVTT

00:00:20.624 --> 00:00:34.138 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We watch the storm clouds gather.
We’ve seen the signs before.

00:00:34.138 --> 00:00:47.276 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The wind of persecution
Is no stranger to our door.

00:00:47.276 --> 00:01:00.414 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We will face each test with courage,
With Jehovah standing near.

00:01:00.414 --> 00:01:13.302 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And ‘no weapon formed against us’
Will give any cause for fear.

00:01:13.302 --> 00:01:20.267 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We are
one united people,

00:01:21.226 --> 00:01:26.774 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Though we come
from ev’ry land.

00:01:26.774 --> 00:01:33.155 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are
standing firm together,

00:01:34.740 --> 00:01:39.662 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
For Jehovah
makes us stand,

00:01:39.662 --> 00:01:47.461 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
For Jehovah
makes us stand.

00:02:01.183 --> 00:02:14.279 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We wait with calm assurance
For Jehovah, the Most High—

00:02:14.279 --> 00:02:27.501 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The God of our salvation
Whose love will never die.

00:02:27.501 --> 00:02:40.597 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
He will never leave his people,
And his spirit makes us strong.

00:02:40.597 --> 00:02:54.111 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
No, our enemies won’t break us.
To Jehovah we belong!

00:02:55.529 --> 00:03:02.202 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We are
one united people,

00:03:02.202 --> 00:03:08.584 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Though we come
from ev’ry land.

00:03:08.584 --> 00:03:13.547 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We are
standing firm together,

00:03:13.547 --> 00:03:21.889 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For Jehovah
makes us stand.

00:03:21.889 --> 00:03:28.479 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We stand firm together;
Unafraid we face the crowd.

00:03:28.479 --> 00:03:41.325 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
And these hearts that beat within us
We have given to our God.

